item.title: [508] Error Message? [508]
item.dc:creator: @roguex roguex
item.description:
@roguex wrote:

The error is obvious it couldn’t find a core class.

Error conditions like this are not worth spending time on. There could be tens if not hundreds of reasons.

Some of the possible reasons could require that you re-install java or even parts of the OS or even hardware.
